							<h2>What is PPC?</h2>
							<p>PPC is one of the popular internet marketing strategies that involves posting an advertisement on the pages of a search engine or on its network websites. The advertisement gets displayed when the visitor searches for a specific keyword or keywords. The advertiser pays only when the visitor clicks on the ad. Once the visitor clicks on the ad he is directed to the landing page.</p>

							<h2>Why PPC?</h2>
							<p>Today PPC is one of the most popular methods of introducing a product in the market. While it's true you should always be optimizing your website to rank well in organic searches, PPC can yield valuable insights that help your business better position its online marketing.</p>

							<h2>Why WebEnrich?</h2>
